<?xml version="1.0" encoding="UTF-8"?><song><hymn_number>679</hymn_number>
<author>lǚ xiǎo mǐn</author>
<lyrics>[V1]
 zhǔ dào shì shàng lái, shòu kǔ shì wèi wǒ. zhǔ bèi shí zì jià, jiān nán shì wèi wǒ.
 zhǔ dīng shí zì jià, téng tòng shì wèi wǒ. shì wèi wǒ shì wèi wǒ. wǒ ná shén me wèi zhǔ huó?
 zhǔ zhǐ yào wǒ de xīn, wán quán guī xiàng tā. zhǔ zhǐ yào wǒ de yǎn, dān dān yǎng wàng tā.
 zhǔ zhǐ yào wǒ de ěr, cháng tīng zhǔ shuō huà. gào sù wǒ bié wàng jì, tiān shàng cái shì yǒng yuǎn de jiā.</lyrics>
<title>zhǔ dào shì shàng lái 迦南679</title>
</song>